		</span>
		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  <a href="mailto:soulskill@slashdot.org" rel="nofollow">Soulskill</a>
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-63144335" datetime="on Sunday September 13, 2020 @06:58PM">on Sunday September 13, 2020 @06:58PM</time>
		
		
			 from the <span class="dept-text">write-once-run-anywhere</span> dept.
		
		</span>
